name: Good News Astronaut #1
description: At Good News Ventures, we invest in pre-seed/seed technology companies founded by true grit entrepreneurs. We back passionate and determined founders as they develop impressive ideas into prominent businesses. We admire those who embrace risk and aren't afraid to break with convention.
